---
title: Pan-fried Duck with Garlicky Greens & Apple with Roasted Potatoes
description: We love a Duck with Greens and Potatoes and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roasted-duck-b0f94a23-634afdf6.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/roasted-duck-5d404e84d6292e001713c76b-846d0c34.pdf
